# Download LineageOS source with patches(local_manifests)
 Refer https://github.com/LineageOS/android/tree/lineage-15.1
 $ git clone https://github.com/shripal17/local_manifests .repo/local_manifests -b oreo
 $ repo sync

# Build for Raspberry Pi3
 https://github.com/shripa17/device_brcm_rpi3/tree/oreo

Use -j[n] option on sync & build steps, if build host has a good number of CPU cores.

Graphics HAL of this build : https://github.com/anholt/mesa/wiki/VC4
